			},
					1497: {
				id_comment: 1497,
				source_str: '✻',
				caption: '',
				content: "Since Adam was the first father of the whole human race, not merely of the Jews, the reference here is probably to one of the later patriarchs; the ‘spokesmen’ may be Moses and Aaron (cf. Num. 20.12), or the false prophets of a later time."
